{
  "id": "5c7611b60737dd00171d3cb1",
  "title": "1分間シンキングタイム",
  "created": 1551241658,
  "updated": 1570713454,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5c7611b60737dd00171d3cb1",
      "text": "1分間シンキングタイム",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551241658,
      "updated": 1551241658
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7611c5aff09e0000f361ce",
      "text": "[質疑応答]の時間の冒頭に1分間の[シンキングタイム]を用意し、その間、発表者が沈黙を守る手法。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551241669,
      "updated": 1551242263
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7611f0aff09e0000f361d0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551241713,
      "updated": 1551241713
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7612ddaff09e0000f361da",
      "text": "よくある質疑応答の問題点",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551241949,
      "updated": 1551241954
    },
    {
      "id": "5c761227aff09e0000f361d2",
      "text": "\tよくある質疑応答では「誰か質問のある人〜」と呼びかけ、手を挙げた人に当て、対話が始まる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551241767,
      "updated": 1551241864
    },
    {
      "id": "5c76129daff09e0000f361d6",
      "text": "\t質問を考えようとしていた人は、自分の考えが整理される前に中断される。対話を聞きたいから。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551241886,
      "updated": 1551242278
    },
    {
      "id": "5c761499aff09e0000f361e5",
      "text": "\t質問に不慣れな人は、自分の考えを整理して質問を作るのに時間が必要。」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551242393,
      "updated": 1551242413
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7612a5aff09e0000f361d7",
      "text": "\t対話が終わるとすぐ「次の質問の人〜」と呼びかけるので、考える時間がない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551241894,
      "updated": 1551242428
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7612d4aff09e0000f361d9",
      "text": "\tずっとコンテンツが流れていたのでは聞くのに精一杯で考えをまとめる時間がない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551241941,
      "updated": 1551241947
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7611f0aff09e0000f361d1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551241713,
      "updated": 1551241713
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7612e6aff09e0000f361dc",
      "text": "改善策",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551241958,
      "updated": 1551241962
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7612eaaff09e0000f361dd",
      "text": "\tまず1分間のシンキングタイムを開始する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551241962,
      "updated": 1551242216
    },
    {
      "id": "5c761309aff09e0000f361df",
      "text": "\t\t質問のある人は手を挙げる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551241994,
      "updated": 1551242060
    },
    {
      "id": "5c76134caff09e0000f361e0",
      "text": "\t\t「ではあなたは3番ね」と番号を振る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551242061,
      "updated": 1551242073
    },
    {
      "id": "5c761358aff09e0000f361e1",
      "text": "\tシンキングタイムが終わったら「じゃあ1番の人〜」と順番に質問を聞いて答える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551242073,
      "updated": 1551242094
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7612e4aff09e0000f361db",
      "text": "\t全部終わったらまたシンキングタイムに入る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551241956,
      "updated": 1551242102
    },
    {
      "id": "5c761370aff09e0000f361e2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551242097,
      "updated": 1551242097
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7614e1aff09e0000f361e7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551242466,
      "updated": 1551242466
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7611baaff09e0000f361cc",
      "text": "講演[エンジニアの知的生産術と体育型授業]で考案して試してみた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551241658,
      "updated": 1551241678
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7611bbaff09e0000f361cd",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/5ccc3017b27bf0c37b0d9ce1e4844fb0]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551241659,
      "updated": 1551242468
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7614e3aff09e0000f361e9",
      "text": "1分間のシンキングタイム中は、発表者も黙ってなければならない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551242468,
      "updated": 1551242473
    },
    {
      "id": "5c7614e8aff09e0000f361ea",
      "text": "静寂の不安に負けて喋ると意味がない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1551242473,
      "updated": 1551242491
    },
    {
      "id": "5d9d7f21aff09e0000c6c9e4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1570602785,
      "updated": 1570602785
    },
    {
      "id": "5d9f2f45aff09e00007399ea",
      "text": "反響",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1570713414,
      "updated": 1570713423
    },
    {
      "id": "5d9f2f4eaff09e00007399ec",
      "text": "\t> #BPStudy 135回 で  @nishio から伝授された「[キャッチボールプレゼン]」、何度かやってどれも質問バンバン出て大成功しているので、感謝しかない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1570713423,
      "updated": 1570713435
    },
    {
      "id": "5d9f2f46aff09e00007399eb",
      "text": "\t\t[@shimizukawa https://twitter.com/shimizukawa/status/1182259587082153985]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1570713415,
      "updated": 1570713453
    },
    {
      "id": "5d9f2f6eaff09e00007399ef",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1570713454,
      "updated": 1570713454
    },
    {
      "id": "5d9d7f21aff09e0000c6c9e5",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1570602785,
      "updated": 1570602789
    },
    {
      "id": "5d9d7f25aff09e0000c6c9e7",
      "text": "\t[slidoスタイル]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1570602789,
      "updated": 1570602799
    },
    {
      "id": "5d9d7f23aff09e0000c6c9e6",
      "text": "\t\t上記の実験の時には質問が「挙手、口頭」だった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1570602787,
      "updated": 1570602846
    },
    {
      "id": "5d9d7f5eaff09e0000c6c9e9",
      "text": "\t\tそもそもそれも電子化したら良いのではないか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1570602846,
      "updated": 1570602846
    },
    {
      "id": "5d9d7f6baff09e0000c6c9ea",
      "text": "\t\tsli.doを使う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1570602859,
      "updated": 1570602864
    },
    {
      "id": "5d9d7f3eaff09e0000c6c9e8",
